c: 20
v: 121
t: "fakl adam whwa' min alshajarat alty nhahma allah enha, fankshft lahuma ewrathma, wakanat mstwrtan ean aeynhma, fakhdha ynzean min waraq ashjar aljanat wylsqanh elyhma; lystra ma ainkashaf min ewrathma, wakhalaf adam 'amr rbh, fghwa balakl min alshajarat alty nhah allah ean alaiqtirab mnha"